          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:14px">Copy each prompt and paste it into <strong style="color:var(--cyan)">hailuoai.com</strong> to generate your anime video</p>
          <div class="prompt-grid" id="promptList"></div>
